metadata.description: Moon Birds Victorian is a project of 700 NFTs inside. Our NFTs are very unique and it's on ETH blockchain. Don't forget, it's just a beginning for our future. You can use your NFTs for your profile picture. If you on this stage you are extremely lucky. First come first served. It's a free project so we only expect your support from your heart. Our goal is to get biggest community you can see and go to the moon with it. We want to make a decision about our project's future by considering all of your thoughts.
